Command        Description                              Example
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
df             Display disk space usage.                df
df -h          Display disk space in human-readable format. df -h
df -a          Include dummy file systems in the output. df -a
df -T          Show the filesystem type.                 df -T
df -i          Display inode information.                df -i
df --total     Display a grand total of all filesystems. df --total
